<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id914568fa-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s9624"><num value="9624">§ 9624.</num><heading> Termination</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id914568fb-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s9624/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The authorities provided under this subchapter terminate on <date date="2031-12-31">December 31, 2031</date>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id914568fc-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s9624/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Termination of Corporation</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Corporation shall terminate on the date on which the portfolio of the Corporation is liquidated.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id914568fd-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/254/dF/tII/s1424">Pub. L. 115–254, div. F, title II, § 1424</ref>, <date date="2018-10-05">Oct. 5, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/3499">132 Stat. 3499</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/119/60/dH/tLXXXVII/s8744">Pub. L. 119–60, div. H, title LXXXVII, § 8744</ref>, <date date="2025-12-18">Dec. 18, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/1963">139 Stat. 1963</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id914568fe-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id914568ff-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id91456900-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2025—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/119/60">Pub. L. 119–60</ref> substituted “<date date="2031-12-31">December 31, 2031</date>” for “7 years after <date date="2018-10-05">October 5, 2018</date>”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
